### ============================================================
### CRM MCP Service - HTTP API 测试
###
### 用 VSCode REST Client (humao.rest-client) 或 IntelliJ IDEA
### 的 HTTP Client 插件打开本文件。点击 "### xxx" 标题上方的
### "Send Request" 即可逐条执行。
###
### 启动服务（另一个终端）：
###     cd crm_mcp
###     python -m crm_mcp                    # 监听 0.0.0.0:8001
###     # 或自定义端口：
###     $env:CRM_MCP_PORT = 18765; python -m crm_mcp
###
### 协议要点
### ---------
### MCP Streamable HTTP 是有状态协议：
###   1) 先 POST /mcp 发 initialize，请求会得到 Mcp-Session-Id header
###   2) 同一个 session id 继续发 notifications/initialized
###   3) 之后所有 tools/call / resources/read 都必须带这个 header
###
### 会话保持机制
### -------------
### 第一个请求用 `# @name initSession` 命名；后续请求通过
###   {{initSession.response.headers.Mcp-Session-Id}}
### 直接引用上一个请求返回的响应头（不需要 > {% %} 脚本块，
### 兼容性更好）。
###
### 完整调试（看每个 tool 的 schema、试 Prompt / Resource）请用
### 官方 Inspector：
###     npx @modelcontextprotocol/inspector http://localhost:8001/mcp
### ============================================================


### ===== Variables =====
@host = http://localhost:8001
@contentType = application/json
@accept = application/json, text/event-stream
@sessionId = {{initSession.response.headers.Mcp-Session-Id}}


### ============================================================
### 1. 初始化 MCP 会话（必须先跑，拿到 Mcp-Session-Id）
###    响应头中的 Mcp-Session-Id 会被后续请求自动引用
### ============================================================
# @name initSession
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {"name": "rest-client", "version": "1.0"}
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 2. 发送 initialized 通知（按 MCP 规范必须）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "notifications/initialized"
}


### ============================================================
### 3. 列出所有可用工具（28 个）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list"
}


### ============================================================
### 4. 列出所有客户（默认 markdown）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_list_customers",
    "arguments": {
      "limit": 5,
      "response_format": "markdown"
    }
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 5. 按 ID 获取客户 C-000001（JSON 格式）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 4,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_get_customer",
    "arguments": {
      "customer_id": "C-000001",
      "response_format": "json"
    }
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 6. 按行业过滤客户（关键字："金融"）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_list_customers",
    "arguments": {
      "query": "金融",
      "industry": "finance",
      "response_format": "markdown"
    }
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 7. 列出所有商机（带分页 + 排序）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 6,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_list_opportunities",
    "arguments": {
      "stage": "negotiation",
      "min_amount": 100000,
      "sort_by": "amount",
      "sort_order": "desc",
      "limit": 10,
      "response_format": "json"
    }
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 8. 创建客户
###    响应体里会带新客户的 id；用 {{createCustomer.response.body...}}
###    解析在后续请求中需要时使用
### ============================================================
# @name createCustomer
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 7,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_create_customer",
    "arguments": {
      "params": {
        "name": "REST Client 测试客户",
        "industry": "internet",
        "tier": "standard",
        "status": "prospect",
        "owner": "rest-client"
      },
      "response_format": "json"
    }
  }
}

> {%
  // 解析响应中的新客户 ID 写入全局变量
  try {
    const body = JSON.parse(response.body);
    const text = body?.result?.content?.[0]?.text || "";
    const data = JSON.parse(text);
    if (data?.data?.id) {
      client.global.set("newCustomerId", data.data.id);
    }
  } catch (e) {
    // 静默失败，下方请求会因变量为空而失败，方便发现
  }
%}


### ============================================================
### 9. 更新刚创建的客户（依赖 #8 的 newCustomerId 全局变量）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 8,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_update_customer",
    "arguments": {
      "customer_id": "{{newCustomerId}}",
      "params": {
        "status": "active",
        "tier": "key",
        "notes": "由 .http 测试更新"
      },
      "response_format": "json"
    }
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 10. 删除刚创建的客户
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 9,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_delete_customer",
    "arguments": {
      "customer_id": "{{newCustomerId}}"
    }
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 11. 错误路径：删除不存在的客户（应返回 [CRM_NOT_FOUND]）
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 10,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "crm_delete_customer",
    "arguments": {
      "customer_id": "C-999999"
    }
  }
}


### ============================================================
### 12. 读取 crm://overview 资源
### ============================================================
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Mcp-Session-Id: {{sessionId}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 11,
  "method": "resources/read",
  "params": {
    "uri": "crm://overview"
  }
}


